name: R4-map-group-type-mode-for-R5
title: Cross-version VS for R4.StructureMapGroupTypeMode for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/map-group-type-mode|4.0.1 for use in FHIR R5. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R4 to R5.
